my life's been all Jekyll and no Hyde.

6
00:00:16,766 --> 00:00:18,392
My brother would be so disappointed.

7
00:00:18,518 --> 00:00:21,186
Don't forget,
tell the universe what you need.

8
00:00:21,312 --> 00:00:23,897
I really need...to kill somebody.

9
00:00:24,024 --> 00:00:25,941
I've been waiting a long time for this.

10
00:00:33,199 --> 00:00:34,116
What the fuck?

11
00:00:34,242 --> 00:00:37,703
I'll be OK. I followed the code.
The stalk was good.

12
00:00:37,829 --> 00:00:40,456
I'm just a little rusty
since killing my brother.

13
00:00:40,582 --> 00:00:43,625
Debra can't sleep
in an empty house any more.

14
00:00:43,752 --> 00:00:46,336
I guess that's what happens
when your fianc? tries to slice you up

15
