18
00:00:52,761 --> 00:00:55,429
You just got to look her in the eyes
to know she's not right.

19
00:00:55,555 --> 00:00:58,098
- Excuse me, are you...
- What the fuck are you doing?

20
00:00:58,224 --> 00:01:01,894
