Right, bitch?

87
00:07:31,868 --> 00:07:33,702
Fucking people don't want our help.

88
00:07:35,496 --> 00:07:38,373
Shit. She had a little girl.

89
00:07:38,499 --> 00:07:39,541
I know.

90
00:07:42,086 --> 00:07:43,712
This stuff never gets to you?

91
00:07:45,423 --> 00:07:47,799
I'm more of a "crying on the inside"
kind of guy.

92
00:07:47,925 --> 00:07:51,470
Wow. He makes the Ice-Truck Killer
look like a goddamn artist.

93
00:07:56,726 --> 00:07:58,310
Sorry, Morgan.

94
00:07:58,436 --> 00:08:00,061
What?

95
00:08:00,188 --> 00:08:01,605
I'm so over that.

96
00:08:03,524 --> 00:08:05,066
You just prove it to me.

97
00:08:05,193 --> 00:08:06,568
You can't.

98
00:08:06,694 --> 00:08:09,404
You're just fucking with me!

99
00:08:11,824 --> 00:08:13,867
I'm gonna have to put you on hold.

100
00:08:17,330 --> 00:08:18,413
Fianc?.

101
00:08:18,539 --> 00:08:21,541
Incarnate. Couldn't pick a worse time, right?

102
00:08:22,877 --> 00:08:23,919
Hey, Esmee.

103
00:08:24,045 --> 00:08:27,047
How about you take off,
let me handle this?

104
00:08:29,091 --> 00:08:31,843
I couldn't let you do that.

105
00:08:31,969 --> 00:08:35,597
I'll write up the report and email it to you
for signature.

106
00:08:35,723 --> 00:08:36,890
OK?

107
00:08:42,730 --> 00:08:47,108
I want Morgan to report to me first thing
in the morning about that bar fight of hers.

108
00:08:47,235 --> 00:08:48,610
Maria...

109
00:08:49,695 --> 00:08:50,862
I owe you.

110
00:08:59,830 --> 00:09:02,249
In there!

111
00:09:05,419 --> 00:09:07,170
Somebody else get in there now!

112
00:09:21,602 --> 00:09:23,770
Mommy!

113
00:09:28,484 --> 00:09:30,527
Seeing her mother that way.

114
00:09:30,653 --> 00:09:33,613
Can you imagine that?

115
00:09:33,739 --> 00:09:36,157
I can't even go there, Angel.

116
00:09:50,798 --> 00:09:53,008
This one's on us, man.

117
00:09:53,134 --> 00:09:57,762
If I had killed Chino last night,
that little girl's mother would still be alive.

118
00:10:16,741 --> 00:10:18,950
I gotta find Chino before he finds me.

119
00:10:23,080 --> 00:10:26,374
...bringing to an even dozen
the number of bodies found offshore.

120
00:10:26,500 --> 00:10:28,877
I have to focus, tune everything out.

121
00:10:29,003 --> 00:10:32,130
So far, the authorities
have no clue as to the criminal.

122
00:10:32,256 --> 00:10:36,885
If I don't, being linked to my bodies of work
will be the least of my worries.

123
00:10:38,429 --> 00:10:40,347
Shit. Little Chino?

124
00:10:40,473 --> 00:10:43,475
He was out there.
The timing could be better.

125
00:10:46,437 --> 00:10:48,855
Yeah, plus I don't have my tools.

126
00:10:50,149 --> 00:10:53,443
It does give me the chance
to tie up one massive loose end.

127
00:11:06,540 --> 00:11:10,043
- It's you, Sergeant.
- Who else you got following you?

128
00:11:11,629 --> 00:11:12,837
Apparently no one.

129
00:11:16,342 --> 00:11:19,886
Go ahead. Try it. I've been waiting.

130
00:11:20,930 --> 00:11:22,889
This neighborhood...

131
00:11:23,015 --> 00:11:24,724
it's full of crazies.

132
00:11:26,310 --> 00:11:28,395
I'd lock my doors.

133
00:11:42,451 --> 00:11:45,203
Bathroom's all yours.

134
00:11:45,329 --> 00:11:47,372
Kind of always was.

135
00:11:52,962 --> 00:11:55,338
We run out of glasses?

136
00:11:55,464 --> 00:11:56,715
Clean ones.

137
00:11:56,841 --> 00:12:01,136
Come here a sec. I found a couple of places
on craigslist you should check out.

138
00:12:01,262 --> 00:12:04,013
Got two bedrooms, two baths,
limited water views,

139
00:12:04,140 --> 00:12:06,266
- has its own gym.
- Hate it.

140
00:12:06,767 --> 00:12:08,268
